POD1000000017_S0000229	inventing and perfecting blues rhythm, blues ideas, blues expression, the expression of
POD1000000017_S0000231	of a fully human black self in American popular art.
POD1000000017_S0000233	He had a kind of confidence that most people would never have heard coming from a black person before.
