YOU1000000035_S0000111	that I've got for them. They survive on very little actually. It's not true to say that they're big dogs and you've got to feed them 2-3-4 pounds of meat a day.
YOU1000000035_S0000112	No, they survive on quite a small amount of food.
YOU1000000035_S0000113	Maybe that's because of their breeding and their having to be up in the mountains.
