YOU1000000035_S0000148	and they worked very hard on her but unfortunately she didn't survive and all they'd got left were these three puppies and the villagers were absolutely heartbroken.
YOU1000000035_S0000149	but the Turks don't recognise any dog called an Anatolian Shepherd Dog.
