YOU1000000035_S0000164	and if that doesn't work he will follow through.
YOU1000000035_S0000166	in animal behaviour patterns.
YOU1000000035_S0000167	until it gets to the point where he has to do what animal behaviour insists that he must do, which is to pick it up and give it a good thumping.
YOU1000000035_S0000168	which is not acceptable in today's modern world. In today's modern world that will make him a dangerous dog, which he doesn't understand.
