YOU1000000035_S0000170	don't do that, I've said I told you not to do that. I've followed all the behaviour lines.
YOU1000000035_S0000172	It isn't just physical strength. You need them to know what you want them to do.
YOU1000000035_S0000173	When we had our first dogs, they knew that I didn't want them to behave in a certain way at a certain place. What they did know was...
YOU1000000035_S0000174	They had somewhere where they could do that. Always our dogs have had somewhere where they could guard.
YOU1000000035_S0000175	Our dogs here, we've got a bride away at the side, they guard. They run up and down and they shout and they scream if anybody goes by. That's what they do.
YOU1000000035_S0000176	When we go out from here, they know that that behaviour is not acceptable.
